    "en": {
      "title": "The things that electricity can do are given out",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy, said in Parliament that even the functions that the Ceylon Electricity Board can do have been given to private institutions.",
        "Accordingly, the minister also mentioned that when there were enough workers to provide services such as cutting branches, providing new connections, disconnecting connections, these services were given to private companies.",
        "He said that attention should be paid in this regard while restructuring the Electricity Board."
      ],
